*****UP TO $15,000.00 IN CONCESSIONS***** Certain Conditions Apply
This is a rare opportunity to purchase a home with a 3.6% mortgage rate included. Assume a mortgage with ROAM  today and save $900 monthly. 
Welcome Home! Come and experience this beautiful home in the Avion Connection West neighborhood. Two story living. Very open and comfortable floorplan which feels spacious in every aspect of its design. Very light and bright, upgrades throughout! The kitchen and bathrooms feature upgraded granite countertops, a large center island an stainless steel appliances. The layout is great for gathering and hanging out with loved ones while preparing a culinary masterpeice. Upstairs you will discover a vry large main bedroom which offers a retreat, large walki in closet, and bathroom, a full sized bathroom in the hallway,convenient laundry room and two other nice sized bedrooms. This home provides plenty of space and functionality for the whole family. This exceptional home not only offers a warm and inviting interior, but is also conveniently located to amenities just a few steps away where you cn enjoy the clubhouse. Here you can enjoy a swim in the pool to cool off on hot summer days or enjoy the hot tube on cool summer nights, or take a peaceful leisurly stroll in nature on the nearby walking trails. This neighborhood offers quick access to Downtown Denver, DIA, esteemed schools, shopping, restaurants and entertainment. Enjoy the best of both worlds, a serene neighborhood retreat and enjoy vibrant city life nearby. This is a meticulously maintained home and lovingly cared for. This home encompasses everything you want n a home, which is a perfect blend of style, convenience and most of all comfort. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity for you and your family. This one wont last long, schedule a showing today and make this beautiful home your own.SELLER OFFERING UP TO 3% OF PURCHASE PRICE IN CONCESSIONS. CONDITIONS APPLY
